Name: Moncrieff
Description: The Division of Moncrieff consists of part of the Gold Coast City Council.
ProductsAndIndustry: Tourism and associated industries and a variety of small industries.
NameDerivation: Named in honour of Gladys Lillian Moncrieff, 1892-1976, light opera and musical comedy singer.
DemographicRating: Provincial - outside capital cities, but with a majority of enrolment in major provincial cities
